  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a wok or large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add garlic and ginger, stir-frying for 1 minute.",
    "Add herbs and stir-fry for another minute.",
    "Add noodles and cook for 2-3 minutes, or until slightly tender.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together soy sauce, coconut aminos, salt, pepper, and tempering spice blend.",
    "Pour the sauce over the noodles and stir-fry for 1 minute.",
    "Add Manchego cheese and stir-fry until melted and well combined.",
    "Transfer the noodles to a wooden board and serve immediately."
